data.description: Waterfront views, New 4 bedroom Available! A stunning home in a highly desired community with 4 bedrooms, 2 baths, and a breathtaking water view. Brand new lanai for soaking in the water view. Great location near major attractions and beaches. Perfect for families seeking an ideal living experience!
